caption.p: Effect of the dietary inclusion of Hermetia illucens larvae on the concentration of amino acid fermentation products in the colonic digesta of pigs: biogenic amines ( a), ammonia ( b), and phenolic and indole compounds ( c). The values are means ± SEM ( n = 8). Asterisks indicated statistical differences between different group (One-way ANOVA with a Tukey post hoc test): * P < 0.05
